item.title: How do i get onto a hamachi server?
item.dc:creator: @Fluxedaway Fluxedaway
item.description:
@Fluxedaway wrote:

  1. Download hamachi at www.hamachincc
  2. Get the server details (Ip, network name, network password, etc.)
  3. Make sure the server is online
  4. Make sure you’re alread connected into the server network
  5. If you haven’t already, create an account
  6. Put in server ip the server ip (obvious)
  7. Enjoy the server

Hope i helped :).
